<%- include("header") -%>
  <!-- TITLE -->
  <div class="title">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><p class="logo-text">EDEMO</p></a>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h1 class="moto">Amplifying <br> your <br>voice</h1>
        <form class="login-form-home" action="/login" method="get">
          <button type="submit" class="login-btn" name="button">LOGIN</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div id="features" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="false">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <img class="feature-img" src="images/image1.png" alt="">
              <h2 class="feature-text">Host Your Elections</h2>
              <p class="feature-desc">You can create your own poll to find your next leader or for making any choice.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="feature-img" src="images/image2.png" alt="">
              <h2 class="feature-text">Secure</h2>
              <p class="feature-desc">We are providing you with a secure interface, allows only verified or known users to vote.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="feature-img" src="images/image3.png" alt="">
              <h2 class="feature-text">Good for analysis</h2>
              <p class="feature-desc">You can use this to find interests of the people.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img src="images/image4.png" alt="">
              <h2 class="feature-text">Register on EDEMO now</h2>
              <form action="/register" method="get">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg feature-btn">Register</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#features" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
          </button>
          <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#features" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="aboutHR">
  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <div class="about-section">
    <h2 class="about">About Website</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <p class="about-desc">Welcome you to a portal where you can have fun, where you can also take important decisions, you can also use this portal for purpose of analysis and many more other things. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <p class="about-desc">You can create your own polls, you can vote on public polls and all this is done in a very secure way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <p class="about-desc">We are taking care of security of your data, your selections and also maintaining privacy of the comments that you make.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <p class="about-desc">Conducting elections on a booth is a good idea but it involves lot of man power and wealth. This website can be efficient for election purpose.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FEEDBACK -->

  <div class="feedback-section">
    <h2 class="feedback-header">We will be improving your experience on the website, if you have been through any query, feel free to report</h2>
    <h3 class="feedback-sub">Here are our socials</h3>
    <button type="button" class="social-btn insta" name="button"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i> Instagram</button>
    <button type="button" class="social-btn twitter" name="button"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i> Twitter</button>
    <button type="button" class="social-btn mail" name="button"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Gmail</button>
  </div>
  <%- include("footer") -%>